# ─── Supabase Edge Function secrets (set via `supabase secrets set`) ─
# DO NOT put these in any frontend env file — these stay server-side.
#
#   supabase secrets set FIXED_OTP=1234
#   supabase secrets set SUPABASE_JWT_SECRET=...    # Project Settings → API → JWT Secret
#   supabase secrets set GOOGLE_VISION_API_KEY=...  # GCP Console
#
# SUPABASE_URL and SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY are auto-injected by Supabase.
